---
title: Herby Chicken & Creamy Brussels Sprout Salad with Cheddar Fries
description: Let’s take tender chicken breast and toss it in a blend of herby spices. Next, we’ll sear it to juicy perfection. Lastly, for the ultimate sweet and savoury sensation, we’ll drizzle it with honey and glaze it all over. Pair it with a crunchy sprout and apple salad and a helping of cheesy fries, who knew pork could be elevated so easily?
